&lt;div class='post-intro'>&lt;/div>&lt;div class='post-body'>&lt;h3>가이드&lt;/h3>&lt;/div>
&lt;div style="margin:40px 0;padding:30px;background:#f8f9fa;border:2px solid #0071e3;border-radius:20px;text-align:center;">
 &lt;p style="font-weight:800;color:#222;font-size:18px;">🛒 "등산용품" 추천 상품 및 가격 비교&lt;/p>
